				<td colspan="2"><span>You can chat a little more easily if you remapp your hotbutton keys to F1-F10.  You need to pick other keys for group member targetting (I did ctrl-F1 -ctrl-F10).  You can then build up a chat sentence in between twisting, since the F-keys do not affect the chat.
<br />

<br />
Every class has a downside.  Bards have low DPS and also can't taunt well at all. I think low taunt is great in a lot of situations.  I can HoS (resist debuff) and slow a mob on a pull and almost any class can pull aggro from me.  But this can be a disdvantage.
<br />

